<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-3 scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
      Sound familiar?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
      Three thoughts every performance marketer has had this month.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <figure class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
          &ldquo;My Meta dashboard says 4.1x ROAS. My Shopify says it&rsquo;s barely 2x.
          <%= link_to "Which one is real?",
                article_path("platform-reports-dont-match"),
                class: "underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-600" %>&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
Every performance marketer, monthly
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
          &ldquo;GA4 attribution
          <%= link_to "dropped from 7 models to 1",
                article_path("ga4-attribution-models-removed"),
                class: "underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-600" %>.
          Now I can&rsquo;t compare anything.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
Anyone migrating from UA, ongoing
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
          &ldquo;Dreamdata wants
          <%= link_to "$750/mo",
                article_path("dreamdata-pricing"),
                class: "underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-600" %>.
          Rockerbox wants a
          <%= link_to "6-month sales cycle",
                article_path("rockerbox-alternatives"),
                class: "underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-600" %>.
          Triple Whale is
          <%= link_to "e-com only",
                article_path("mbuzz-vs-triple-whale"),
                class: "underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-600" %>.
          There&rsquo;s nothing in between.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
Mid-market marketers, the gap
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12 scroll-animate" data-controller="scroll-reveal">
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        If any of those sound like your week, the 3-minute score will tell you exactly where you sit.
      </p>
      <%= link_to "Score your attribution &rarr;".html_safe, score_path,
            class: "inline-block px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 rounded-md transition-all" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
